reviewText: I did not get the correct movie inside of the case. The reason it got one star is because it wouldn't let me write a review without a rating. I'm not happy with this product.  I'm not sure what could have happened. But when I noticed I got some documentary about kings, and not Kentucky versus Duke I was a little mad. And the cover specifically showing Kentucky versus Duke.

It was great watching this game again and experiencing the "getting even" aspect of beating Duke. This whole season was a wonderful, unexpected ride for Wildcat fans. I'd like more of the tournament games from '98.
